      <scopecontent encodinganalog="5202_">
    
         <p>Manuscript letter from Ambers Elwyn Watson to Myrl Davis, 2 pages, May 7, 1919, regarding his experiences in World War I, bringing back the 32nd Field Artillery Division from Brest, France, in a record-breaking 22-day round trip, parades and soldiers in New York.</p>  
